imdb.plot outline: Animal videos for kids and babies will have your preschooler laughing and dancing. Come stomp and chomp along to the Mother Goose Club hit song "Dinosaur Stomp," quack with a duck family in "Five Little Ducks," and dance the day away to the classic kids song "Baby Shark". "Animal Songs From Mother Goose Club Playhouse" will keep your little one laughing and singing along.
